            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Licaius Seri <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> miles <lb n="2"/>ex c<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>ho</abbr><ex>rte</ex></expan> I Pa<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>nonioru</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>XXX <expan><abbr>sti</abbr><ex>pendiorum</ex></expan> XVI <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> frater op <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>pie</abbr><ex>tatem</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift befindet sich unterhalb einer Nische mit der Reliefdarstellung eines stehenden Soldaten. Z. 3 (Ende): Buchstabe I klein in E eingefügt. (B): Ritterling; Mattern: Z. 3 (Ende): op(us) p(i)e(tatem).</p>
            </div>
